'''Brian Fraim''' is a ''[[Star Wars]]'' fan who designed the [[Skel]]s in the [[Design An Alien]] contest held in the ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]s''. The entry was given an honorable mention in the 16 years and older category. He was 22 at the time his entry was published.

